Dialogs.Text: LostDecipher2: So, what is your group doing here?
MsMaki95: We are interested in lost software, movies and many other things. ^-^
MsMaki95: Things that people remember existed, but can't be found anymore. u-u
LostDecipher2: I know that, i mean, how did they found this place?
MsMaki95: Oh that Un-n. Well, i don't know how they found it, some friends that were in the group passed me the link and i joined.
MsMaki95: It's interesting, you find something new every day. c:
Thomas B: So she got here by invitation, i will have to look who else is in this place and trace the origin of this invitation.
MsMaki95: You seem like a curious guy, i think they will love to include you in the team if you meet them. n-n
LostDecipher2: Sounds interesting, but i will have to think about it.
